* 1 [[Antonov An-32]] * 1 [[Beechcraft Super King Air|Raytheon Beech King Air 200]] * 1 [[Beechcraft Super King Air|Raytheon Beech King Air B200]] * 1 [[Ilyushin Il-76]]
