'''Dukpu''' is an ethnic group of the [[Central African Republic]], [[Democratic Republic of Congo]] and [[Sudan]]. They speak [[Mid-Southern Banda]], a [[Ubangian language]]. The number of persons in this group exceeds 100,000.

