'''Niger''' is a term taken from the [[Niger River]], which also refers to one of Africa's five political, sports and geographic regions. The other four regions are the [[Sahara (African Region)|Sahara]], [[Congo (African Region)|Congo]], [[Nile (African Region)|Nile]] and the [[Kalahari (African Region)|Kalahari]].

